item.title: About
item.description: My name is Tanner Lueders, and I am a Senior DevOps Engineer that originated out of Software Development. My most recent role involved building highly available cloud infrastructure (Kubernetes), build pipelines (Cloud Build & ArgoCD) and data pipelines (Apache Airflow) to support a Financial Tech data visualization platform. I am currently open for work! Feel free to connect on LinkedIn.
